Essential Information on Food Labels

Food labels should include:

Product name

Brand name

Ingredient list

Net weight or volume

Nutrition facts

Allergen information

Batch or lot number

Manufacturing date

Expiry or "Best Before" date

Storage instructions

Preparation instructions (if applicable)

Manufacturer's name and address

Country of origin

NAFDAC registration number (where applicable)

Barcode



